txt.en: Your mission is to reach the Ekhamâti camp where they are holding prisoners and free any that you can. Then put an end to the executioner before he can harm any more people.
'Are you here to rescue me? I was certain this was the end.'
Find and defeat the Ekhamâti executioner!
'Their suffering is over and the executioner's torment has ended. We should return to Iridír with the news.'
As his chamber opens, the executioner beckons you in. Defeat him!
Your mission is to reach the Ekhamâti camp where they are holding prisoners and free any that you can. Then put an end to the executioner before he can harm any more people.
